      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个状态图，展示FinTech_LedgerService和FinTech_FraudDetection这两个核心系统跟周边组件的依赖关系。LedgerService这边主要是开发者直接对接，然后开发者再去管理基础设施和Kubernetes。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_LedgerService",
        "Developer",
        "Infrastructure",
        "Kubernetes"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，LedgerService指向Developer，Developer再分出两条线分别连到Infrastructure和Kubernetes。那CommonConfig这个组件放在哪里？它跟这些都有关系吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Developer",
        "Infrastructure",
        "Kubernetes",
        "CommonConfig"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，CommonConfig是配置中心，Developer要引用它，Infrastructure也要同步配置，Kubernetes同样需要读取CommonConfig。另外Application这个节点要接在CommonConfig下面。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CommonConfig",
        "Developer",
        "Infrastructure",
        "Kubernetes",
        "Application"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把CommonConfig作为中心节点，连上Developer、Infrastructure、Kubernetes，同时Application从CommonConfig引出。那FinTech_FraudDetection这边怎么关联？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CommonConfig",
        "Application",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "FraudDetection是独立的反欺诈服务，它只跟Application有直接关系，Application调用它的API。所以Application指向FraudDetection，但FraudDetection不直接连CommonConfig。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Application",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，Kubernetes和CommonConfig之间是单向还是双向？实际部署中K8s既要读取配置，配置变更也会触发K8s滚动更新。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Kubernetes",
        "CommonConfig"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "双向的，Kubernetes和CommonConfig互相有连线。这样整个链路就完整了：LedgerService→Developer→Infrastructure/Kubernetes↔CommonConfig→Application→FraudDetection。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Kubernetes",
        "CommonConfig",
        "FinTech_LedgerService",
        "Developer",
        "Infrastructure",
        "Application",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成，所有节点和关系都已画好。FinTech_LedgerService作为入口，经过Developer展开到基础设施层，CommonConfig作为配置枢纽双向连接Kubernetes，最终通过Application延伸到FinTech_FraudDetection。",
